Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看到女王陛下出現呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個，她好像還沒準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子有點可怕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是穿幫可就不得了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日邦格\N是非常注重禮儀的國家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前就有先來通知過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓大人物蒙羞的話\N家臣似乎就得…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切腹一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話會出人命耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是以死謝罪之意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說“們”…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼處理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆弄個冒牌貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有人能模仿\N真白女王那白癡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那天真過頭的態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 面具舞會？\N對不起，過去我太惡劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了引起妳注意而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凪·戴·阿爾泰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了我而死吧，凪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，妳醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有哪裡會痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳很有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德布倫王國女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布蘭·杜·溫德布倫\N駕到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我就是真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須多禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這次突然造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠惶誠恐地\N感謝您寬容地接納
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須多禮，無須多禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是鴇羽巧海頭忠賴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這是貴國的招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須多禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海頭大人，初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真白女王陛下的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自叫加爾德羅貝的學園？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次來訪的一大目的之一\N便是視察學園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能由女王和\N女王的乙HiME帶路的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，拜託妳打雜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是葵妳拜託我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時我都會飛過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話\N留在學園裡面說就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，因為我才剛從外國過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說這是溫德市的某地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德市，怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國有這麼髒亂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這裡果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這種表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎？很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子…不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦，很浪費耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪看過妳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛從國外來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國外？妳也是啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是從阿爾泰來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我還沒問妳叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，晶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾久崎晶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿爾泰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼從這邊上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦\N怎麼可能學得了真白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這一步了還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳為什麼\N要說自己是愛莉卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王也不想當\N真白女王的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也沒有說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟真白女王\N已經定下契約了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳為什麼會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，不要告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟真白約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，相對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡之前發生過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今天一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就負責扮演妳的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個生日真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這附近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於是我的後院了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳不是從外國來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別告訴你我的真面目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，那張肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著吧，驚訝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肖像是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是我生日耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜今天生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等等喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然混在前哨裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥也已經快要用完了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一位太體貼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能被可疑人士盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體也令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要儘早找到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…要給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是一朵小花\N也要給我當禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子大也得有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了買那朵花\N花掉我身上僅剩的錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了送給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你未免也太濫好人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉，想起一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前常常被罵濫好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這樣很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠替別人慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果你\N無論如何都要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你親自送給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以…喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如同剛才說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位多加協助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎蒞臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是學園長夏樹·庫魯格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起為您導覽學園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從這裡爬樓梯會有點辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請從那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得見見王子一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…妳竟然是女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我不適合穿禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會，很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂“人要衣裝”嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對，我聽妮娜說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂啦，螞蟻仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算受到你祝福我也不會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意他人眼光玩耍\N真的很快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久沒有這樣玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從外國來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋，最後一個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，你是來做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這個城市找人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很清楚\N那個人已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很想知道\N那個人在這看過什麼，想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罵我是濫好人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很好騙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑奈緒的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以順利成為乙HiME的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子守住貞操奉獻國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便找個有錢的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就可以快活過一生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的人生計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪亞選帝侯家的少爺\N或許挺不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可別不小心\N失去乙HiME資格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日邦格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個國家沒有乙HiME呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好俊倘的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被他看上的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠順利\N拉攏那個國家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，畢竟情勢如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那個王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王，這樣很不成體統喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到真白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛士長他們拼了命在找了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶大人，辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，少主到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人家猛操心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還害我得扮演這麼麻煩的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不理解少主的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他總是很黏著姊姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我也老是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊織，你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟外頭聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請趁這段時間沖個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算騙得過其他人\N也騙不過我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放…放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我問出妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又為什麼要假扮\N巧海頭王子之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…能否共進晚餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備追她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是巧海頭王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草傳來情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主好像跟\N奇怪的年輕姑娘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶大人，這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一下下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找個地方去一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，大家應該都在找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經以我自己的方式\N充分看夠這個國家和城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何，是個好地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我真正的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起舉城歡慶生日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者改建城堡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有更重要的事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些地方的人的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不工作的人自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒辦法工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有工作可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至有小孩\N因為明天沒有麵包吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而出手行竊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有麵包的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃糖果就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我是非知道不可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是乙HiME？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我跟那種東西混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少主？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對少主做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們以為他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是日邦格將軍家嫡男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽巧海頭忠賴少主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥呢？吃完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳…晶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西，讓我這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人…都是男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是愛情的一種形式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主天生胃就虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME真是\N百聞不如一見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝您的稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也抱持某些疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是為了保障安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是讓女孩子背負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的舊時代科學力\N以及一個國家的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種做法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N乙HiME的存在讓現世得以安定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，就是因為\N有這麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們才會渴望乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME又因不得不回應而痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此，我們嚴格選拔乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，“炎綬的紅玉”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的狀況又該怎麼解釋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的夢想和戀情\N都被硬生生地抽離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都認為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是堅強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎綬的紅玉是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裡並不是為了挑選乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是為了相親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國日邦格今後將暫時貫徹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不干涉西方諸國的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來傳達這一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然各國都派使者過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法具體指出國名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是許多國家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長，非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗地飛翔著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無垢的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負起來神子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白陛下因為不舒服\N所以無法前來送行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了對不起陛下的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我轉告她要當一位好女王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…殿下是…舞衣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦～有緣再會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許還會再來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來我 想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我們也有戲份呢\N（在茜色的天空…）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不服氣\N為什麼我是你的臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是晶的俘虜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是老樣子，這麼親熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被小茜這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
